'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 13''' is the thirteenth issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints, published on [[May 3]], [[1978]].

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 7|''Star Wars'' (1977) 7]] {{C|Part 1}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 1|Man-Gods from Beyond the Stars]]" {{C|Part 8}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 7|The Sword in the Star! Stave 2: Witchworld!]]" {{C|Part 4}}

*A full-color Star Wars mini-poster, the first of a matching pair to be completed [[Star Wars Weekly 14|next issue]].
*Notably, this issue features no competitions or articles.

